title: MisterMusic Show 350 indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show # 350 [2 hours] 192kbps stereo-


On this week's show new music from The Maccabees, The Wombats, Wire, and Siskiyou. Plus a international smash hit from April 1974 is the Oldie of the Week. A song that had a resurgence last year because of a film.

It's over 5 decades of indie, alternative and rock hits... the MisterMusic Show.

Broadcasting weekly and heard globally on RockXS radio.
